{"tid":1830583,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"事實證明，堅持和勇不分，自然杜絕捉鬼，搵到出路","createTime":"2020-01-19T17:08:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T06:44:18.000Z","uid":79724,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e30ca781f0d043ee53defe85d92479e17ea4994b","tid":1830583,"uid":79724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T17:08:06.000Z","msg":"成班黑狗戇鳩鳩，又想學人玩輿論戰，搵隻冇裝嘅便衣指揮官嚟引人私了，仲搵狗喬裝埋阻膠，想製造被害畫面，分化和勇，點知玩出禍。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家好啦，幫我哋完美示範阻膠同狗嘅本質根本一樣，又衝破一個心理關口啦，以後真假阻膠都冇運行。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有嗰啲乜鳩勇武退場論，嘥鳩氣啦。人人都係和，人人都係勇呀，傻閪警畜。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a1343c6f4b8b75f230df761cd611ea38af23de1","tid":1830583,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T17:09:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">殺</span>"},{"pid":"bb0af7ceb090df255a5a8545109938a64d4b9d64","tid":1830583,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T18:37:07.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"b67a0631f486ddc615a07cf653748beb44eb3d13","tid":1830583,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T06:44:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}